com.knowgate.datacopy

Class DataStruct

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • com.knowgate.datacopy.DataStruct
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataStructOrcl, FullTableCopy

    public class DataStruct
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
implements org.xml.sax.ContentHandler

    Copier for Complex Data Structures stored at database.

    This is not a general purpose module, but a custom class tailored to the design constraints of hipergate standard datamodel.
    Version:
    0.6 alpha
